hopobject.body: What are the hours of work? ventolin hfa price cvs The budget on Verbinski’s film is far, far bigger. A couple of years ago, as it started to head over the $250 million mark, Disney pulled the plug and the movie was cancelled. It only got back under way after action sequences were cut and several key figures, including Depp, reportedly agreed to pay deferments while Bruckheimer himself put up “development money”. With the revised budget set at $215 million, shooting resumed.
